songs.title: Oringo
songs.lyrics:

Oringo gbu kwa ewu (hey)
Gbu ewu (hey)
Oringo gbu kwa ewu (origo)
Bgu ewu
Bgu ewu
Bgu ewu

Oringo gbu kwu ewu
Ifuko kwa na men nosi
Nenu
Oyo (ah)
Nwa bu nenu
Kuwa we keep it hundred
High (high)
Oringo gbu kwa ewu there
Ifuko kwa na men nosi
Nenu here
Kupu nwa bu lenu (lenu)

Oringo gbu kwa ewu
(oringo gbu kwa ewu)
Bgu ewu
Bgu ewu
Oringo gbu ewu

[Verse 1: Phyno]
Nnwane open your eyes
O ni dia fu uso
Ewelum gps nnmuwa aadia
Cho uso
Enukwa na mames bu
Ezibgote ntu
Ayin beni te there
Ayin adaia tu ujo (kwa)
Ma gwara gi
Oni ma n ga
Adime kwe akwe akwe
Ka muna oyim kpa ama
Ona tuwarim si owerri
Si aba
Muwa gbasa nu fa
Fa malu kwanu ebe

Nnwane hapu han there
Nekwa kwa pina piram
Ebe ona shaky ya there
Ayin te yen isi nobodo
Ayin na painti ya red

Je pasagodi there
See we keep it hundred
Nnwane hapu ya there
Nnekwa pina piram ebe
Ona shaky ya there
Ayin ti yen si obodo
Ayin ne painti ya red
Ekwo too much
Je pasagodi there
See we keep it hundred

Oyo (ah)
Nwa bu nenu
Kuwa we keep it hundred
High (high)
Oringo gbu kwa ewu there
Ifuko kwa na men nosi
Nenu here
Kupu nwa bu lenu (lenu)
Kuwa we keep it hundred high
Oringo gbu kwa enu
(oringo gbu kwa enu)
Bgu ewu
Bgu ewu
Oringo gbu ewu

[Verse 2: Phyno]
When I kuso the place

Na kupoli na club
With nwa bu figure 8
Nnsiya wetin dey happen
Osim nnwokem hapu
Long as no welu the chair

Ewe puta the money
Oge shaky ya body
Oge bu yungi nnukwu Ichaka
Ha dika lorry
Ega gbanu hundred meters
Ega burunu calories
Emesi na medele
Me I no say you no ri
Nmawun show them the buy
Echi anya kpo yen the buy
And obina emera now
Nnwane eka no far
Till we keep it hundred
Abani till sunset
And anyin na kulicha
Dika anyi bu indi black belt
Nnwane hapu ya there
Nekwa pina piram ebe ona
Shaky ya there
Ayin te yen isi na obodo
Ayin na painti ya red
E kwo too much
Je pasagodi there
See we keep it hundred
Nnwane hapu ya there
Nekwa pina piram ko ona
Shaky ya there
Ayin tiyen isi nobodo
Ayin na painti ya red
E kwo too much
Je pasagodi there
See we keep it hundred

[Chorus]
Kupu oringo gbu kwu ewu

Nwa bu nenu
Kuwa we keep it hundred high (high)
Oringo gbu kwa ewu there

Oringo gbu kwu ewu
